title: `EmitCompilerGeneratedFiles` and `CompilerGeneratedFilesOutputPath` are not present in auto completion
body:
### Issue Description

`EmitCompilerGeneratedFiles` and `CompilerGeneratedFilesOutputPath` are not present in auto completion

They should be added similar to https://github.com/dotnet/msbuild/pull/5728

nodes.body: Could i take up this issue?

@ryan-rozario all yours. Please let us know if you have any trouble.
